00:50:31.460 --> 00:50:34.730
DAYENU-- ENOUGH!

00:50:34.730 --> 00:50:39.500
"WELL, FOR ME THERE ARE NEVER
ENOUGH TASTES OF PASSOVER."

00:50:39.500 --> 00:50:42.300
THERE'S NEVER ENOUGH
TIME WITH FAMILY

00:50:42.300 --> 00:50:44.760
AND CERTAINLY
NEVER ENOUGH MUSIC.

00:50:44.760 --> 00:50:46.800
WE LEAVE YOU WITH ONE FINAL SONG

00:50:46.800 --> 00:50:51.060
"WITHOUT WHICH NO PASSOVER WOULD
BE COMPLETE, ""KHAD GADYO"""

00:50:51.060 --> 00:50:55.230
THE SONG ABOUT A LITTLE GOAT A
FATHER BOUGHT FOR TWO PENNIES.

00:50:55.230 --> 00:50:57.160
I'M THEODORE BIKEL

00:50:57.160 --> 00:51:00.360
AND FROM THE NEW ENGLAND
CONSERVATORY OF MUSIC IN BOSTON

00:51:00.360 --> 00:51:06.830
"I WISH YOU A HAPPY PASSOVER, A
KUSHERN PESACH, CHAG SAMEACH."

00:51:06.830 --> 00:51:09.330
GOOD NIGHT.

